  "texts": [
    "Outcomes were assessed regarding linguistic complexity and cognitive performance as the dependent variables.",
    "Since the results may be influenced by numerous other independent variables, some of them were systematically manipulated to explore the latent space of the models in question.",
    "This approach resulted in a total of 1296 independent trials.",
    "In each trial, LLMs had the opportunity to generate all intermediate responses, not just a final answer, thereby simulating a genuine dialogue.",
    "Given that the contemporary Western LLMs are predominantly trained on English data, the entire experiment was conducted in English."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}